{"title":"8. Infestaciones-2021","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Infectología/8. Infestaciones-2021.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Infestaciones","guid":"xRaPdwIUPt5WIT-hqvciBA","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Sarna","guid":"sixKlDi5sVH4PJFngOJpaQ","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"\\\\/Sarcoptes scabiei\\\\/","guid":"RYx5Lhv-LckN9zJsub5mqg","children":[]},{"id":"3","parent":"1","text":"Transmisión ","guid":"CqLrt49Rr8I1cXiiy6oGZA","children":[{"id":"4","parent":"3","text":"contacto personal íntimo","guid":"MMJjAGhDJrjCKQByckDQcQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"5","parent":"1","text":"Clinica ","guid":"C11p53y245a2sKhLjoTrow","children":[{"id":"6","parent":"5","text":"pápulas y nódulos\\Nintensamente pruriginosos","guid":"vegHJlLADESrTBFzIm0O9Q","children":[]},{"id":"7","parent":"5","text":"surcos correspondientes a los túneles que excava el ácaro, localizados en los\\Nespacios interdigitales, muñecas, tobillos, mamas, área periumbilical y genitales","guid":"TcYVdrqrRAwoFJRGPVpvaA","children":[]},{"id":"8","parent":"5","text":"sarna costrosa y altamente\\Ncontagiosa (sarna noruega","guid":"9MzcK5AklQRlwjOFkmVRig","children":[{"id":"9","parent":"8","text":"adultos de edad avanzada, pacientes\\Ninmunodeprimidos o con síndrome de Down","guid":"p4TdKwMXGE8lUJefxKANxA","children":[]},{"id":"10","parent":"8","text":"lesiones cubiertas de grandes escamas superpuestas","guid":"dJZrCHl75VFd_1fNaiUPxg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"11","parent":"1","text":"diagnóstico","guid":"4gzm9ibFvUFw8uixQ1FUvQ","children":[{"id":"12","parent":"11","text":"identificación microscópica de los ácaros,\\Nhuevos o heces en raspados cutáneos\\Npreparados con aceite de vaselina","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"13","parent":"1","text":"Tratamiento ","guid":"j5-RW_SV4KBb9y1W0vgUxQ","children":[{"id":"14","parent":"13","text":"tratar al paciente y a sus contactos íntimos para\\Neliminar la infestación original","guid":"hLI7P4ukMJxMhmb5NCZmCw","children":[]},{"id":"15","parent":"13","text":"crema de\\Npermetrina al 5%","guid":"pWEN69K4-PxmT6J5uSyHWw","children":[{"id":"16","parent":"15","text":"crema se aplica por la noche a toda la superficie corporal, desde el cuello hasta los\\Ndedos de los pies, incluyendo los genitales y debajo de las uñas de las manos","guid":"h9avhWQdetM8nh4aSzlgfg","children":[]},{"id":"17","parent":"15","text":"se elimina con una ducha o baño 8-14 horas después de la aplicación","guid":"5R9e71DbnpuVMseIIlVFEA","children":[]},{"id":"18","parent":"15","text":"repetido al cabo de 7-10 días","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"19","parent":"13","text":"lavar minuciosamente las ropas, sábanas y cualquier cosa que haya estado en\\Ncontacto con la piel durante la semana o dos semanas precedentes","guid":"Wzg6yKpMR9UOJ-b-G3-FTw","children":[]},{"id":"20","parent":"13","text":"prurito postsarnoso","guid":"","children":[{"id":"21","parent":"20","text":"prurito puede persistir durante semanas\\Ndespués de la erradicación","guid":"9mC4NRUEvNgg3043Lb6P7g","children":[]},{"id":"22","parent":"20","text":"antihistamínicos y glucocorticoides tópicos; en casos más graves\\Npueden administrarse glucocorticoides orales","guid":"","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"23","parent":"0","text":"Piojos","guid":"Kxk2e_mhq5fz-iiHEj6Vaw","children":[{"id":"24","parent":"23","text":"tres tipos de piojos que\\Ninfestan a los humanos","guid":"AEALT3viOE3RA5mKGTTQOA","children":[{"id":"25","parent":"24","text":"piojos de la cabeza (\\\\/Pediculus humanus capitis\\\\/)","guid":"6FLUYtNU_H61qR60cBU-Qw","children":[{"id":"26","parent":"25","text":"viven en el cuello cabelludo y adhieren sus\\Nhuevos (liendres) al tallo piloso proximal","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"27","parent":"24","text":"cuerpo (\\\\/Pediculus humanus corporis\\\\/)","guid":"bxe-mado7PSybxWWeDuMdw","children":[{"id":"28","parent":"27","text":"viven en las costuras de ropas, no en la piel","guid":"Mi11hWmpSzzjY3bJzLcbZA","children":[]},{"id":"29","parent":"27","text":"excoriaciones dan lugar a pápulas costrosas o petequias\\Nlineales en tronco, cuello y porción proximal de los brazos","guid":"tI5X_IsfNcDnXwDqyiLuIQ","children":[]},{"id":"30","parent":"27","text":"máculas cerúleas","guid":"cmPBTg4TjGw1w1_l4ScEYg","children":[{"id":"31","parent":"30","text":"máculas de color azul pardusco secundarias a hemorragia\\Nsubcutánea en lugares en que se alimentan los piojos","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"32","parent":"24","text":"pubis (\\\\/Pthirus pubis\\\\/)","guid":"kHrzLo3cpRfQ_OBiSsjrJQ","children":[{"id":"33","parent":"32","text":"contacto sexual","guid":"x9gwAKtGZge2uP9RXDFqmA","children":[]},{"id":"34","parent":"32","text":"pueden adherirse a otros sitios, como cejas y\\Npestañas (\\\\/Pediculosis ciliaris\\\\/).","guid":"AGZvS9wqypeXP0BGXNHBmw","children":[]},{"id":"35","parent":"32","text":"picor en el área afectada y\\Nmáculas cerúleas","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"36","parent":"23","text":"transmisión","guid":"_Yb6vmo1uCRLldAHgOpEKA","children":[{"id":"37","parent":"36","text":"contacto personal íntimo o por fómites, como\\Nsábanas, ropas o cepillos de pelo","guid":"GpCYapJHZuECfGgIt84K5g","children":[]}]},{"id":"38","parent":"23","text":"Tratamiento ","guid":"LTuGA5WGegy4ozfP_z9D0g","children":[]}]},{"id":"39","parent":"0","text":"Chinches","guid":"5SbG6u6BN5h1ZsVgvfJgpQ","children":[{"id":"40","parent":"39","text":"viven en suelos de madera, paredes,\\Nrespiraderos o mobiliario","guid":"7JudKyrRWoOQ_GSdboTn3A","children":[]},{"id":"41","parent":"39","text":"Clinica ","guid":"rQRH2OzHqVl6pBauOCt2-Q","children":[{"id":"42","parent":"41","text":"alimentarse durante la noche","guid":"eQmMSP5CUdnHrTulmX7AdQ","children":[{"id":"43","parent":"42","text":"No viven en el cuerpo humano","guid":"oXJBXof6kUKnK5x_1OVMUQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"44","parent":"41","text":"picaduras producen pápulas urticariales\\Ndispuestas de una forma lineal característ","guid":"fsHVtDhWgqgJKPGnP--8-g","children":[{"id":"45","parent":"44","text":"picaduras del «desayuno, almuerzo y cena»","guid":"oD882IDlxz3sgxdf7yZnUQ","children":[]},{"id":"46","parent":"44","text":"en la piel expuesta","guid":"ENL6BbbOf7364OWaDav8Uw","children":[]}]},{"id":"47","parent":"41","text":"lesiones son pápulas pruriginosas indoloras similares a la urticaria.","guid":"mpRmV1sn8jQ8quGpql40VQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"48","parent":"39","text":"tratamiento","guid":"3T9SFr-GXCZGO9CS5EFbcw","children":[]}]}]},"node_count":48,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"Infectología","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Infectología","filename":"8. Infestaciones-2021","id":"map_1120","resolved_references":[]}